{
  "stem": "21786.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had to build it from the scratch, from the floor, the walls, the door, the kind of primitive insulation, and the window.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, the wood [INAUDIBLE], whatever else was there, was organized.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very good for-- it was very unusual, for I could stay there, which was strictly forbidden, with Eva together.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from there, we left Theresien.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It depends what you were doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there was a drastic difference between the young people, who could cope with it somehow, and the old people, who were completely out of their normal routine and simply-- they were hungry, and they were undercl-- underclothed, and they were cold.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were-- they lost all their privacy and all their human dignity.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Put together, I mean, into one room, they put-- where we were four, into that room, they would put two dozens of old people, who were just slowly preparing themselves to die, who were doing some kind of menial job, whether it was cleaning the street, or, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know, preparing something in the distribution or in the registration or anything.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As long as they could work, they could get some kind of better food, or a little bit more.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were queues and queues for food which was distributed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And compared to other things, this still wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then we slowly started to realize that the Germans are preparing something else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are grooming this ghetto for probably something that they want to show to the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In other words, want to show to the international and Swiss Red Cross how well, actually, are the Jews being taking care of.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- we were already left.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
